title: Commander Keen FAQ
content:
This had to be done sometime... no longer will annoying newbies have to ask us crummy questions ever again! I have compiled a load of crazy questions for your reading pleasure...

How do I get into the secret level in CK1?
Explore the large city (not the ice city) which can be found at the far right of the map, go to the very bottom of the level to find a teleporter, which will lead you to the secret level.

How do I get into the secret level in CK2?
There is no secret level.

How do I get into the secret level in CK3?
Next to the boss level on the world map, the Loch Ness Monster, also known as 'Messie' will (eventually) pick you up and lead you to a small island.

How do I get into the secret level in CK4?
In the 'Pyramid of the Moons', grab the yellow key, use it to unlock the yellow door (not the door which unlocks the exit, but there's another yellow door), activate the switch and
gather all 12 Inchworms. They will form a giant foot. The giant foot will lead you to the secret level, 'The Pyramid of the Forbidden'.

How do I get into the secret level in CK5?
In the 'Gravitational Damping Hub', don't enter the exit, instead, press down, then jump on the arch in front of the exit. Walk left until Keen falls. Complete the rest of the level,
which will prompt you to leave via the 'Korath III Base' teleporter.

How do I get into the secret level in CK6?
Before entering the final level, wait for the satellite to pick you up.

How do I get into the secret level in Keen Dreams?
There is no secret level. If you have the Shareware Version of Keen Dreams, try level 7 or 8 for a BETA level.

How do I get into the secret level in Commander Keen for Gameboy Color?
There is no secret level.

What are the cheats for CK1, CK2 & CK3?
Press G-O-D to activate God Mode (It must be activated each time you enter a level).
Press G-O-D to active No Clipping on the Map Level. (Allows you to walk through walls)
Press C-T-Space to obtain free objects (Keys, Lives etc.)
Press Alt-Tab throughout the Map Level to walk through levels.
Press F8 in the older versions of the game to corrupt the level which you are currently on.

What are the cheats for CK4, CK5?
Press A-2-Enter to activate debug mode. Debug mode can also be activated by typing
in 'keenXe.exe -nowait' on the DOS Prompt (where X is the corresponding episode).
Throughout the game, try any of these cheats...
F10-D - Demo Mode (Allows you to record demos, But they can't be viewed)
F10-G - God Mode
F10-I - Free Items (Keys, Extra Points, Swimsuit, Items)
F10-J - Jump Cheat (Allows you to fly by pressing jump)
F10-M Memory Usage (View Memory Usage)
F10-N - No Clipping (Allows you to fall through walls, Use Jump Cheat beforehand)
F10-T - Sprite Mode (Allows you to browse through all sprites in the level you are in)
F10-W - Warp (Select which level you wish to play)
F10-Y - Secret Cheat (Allows you to find all the secret areas in the level you are in)
There may be some more cheats than this, but they're quite useless.
Press B-A-T at any time throughout the game (without debug mode) to receive free
objects. Although your score may be reset to zero.
Press E-N-D at any time throughout the game (without debug mode) to view the ending
sequence.

What are the cheats for CK6?
Throughout the game, try any of these cheats...
F10-D - Demo Mode (Allows you to record demos, But they can't be viewed)
F10-G - God Mode
F10-I - Free Items (Keys, Extra Points, Swimsuit, Items)
F10-J - Jump Cheat (Allows you to fly by pressing jump)
F10-M Memory Usage (View Memory Usage)
F10-N - No Clipping (Allows you to fall through walls, Use Jump Cheat beforehand)
F10-T - Sprite Mode (Allows you to browse through all sprites in the level you are in)
F10-W - Warp (Select which level you wish to play)
F10-Y - Secret Cheat (Allows you to find all the secret areas in the level you are in)
There may be some more cheats than this, but they're quite useless.
Press B-A-T at any time throughout the game (without debug mode) to receive free
objects. Although your score may be reset to zero.
Press E-N-D at any time throughout the game (without debug mode) to view the ending
sequence.

What are the cheats for Keen Dreams?
Throughout the game, try any of these cheats...
F10-G - God Mode
F10-I - Free Items (Keys, Extra Points, Items)
F10-J - Jump Cheat (Allows you to fly by pressing jump)
F10-M Memory Usage (View Memory Usage)
F10-W - Warp (Select which level you wish to play)

What are the cheats for Commander Keen for Gameboy Color?
There are no cheats. If you have a cheating device, visit it's website.

Isn't Commander Keen 7 released yet?
No, it is not.

Isn't the Gameboy Color version the seventh CK episode?
I said... NO!

Uh... Isn't Keen Dreams the seventh episode of CK?
GOD NO! Keen Dreams is episode 3.5, which falls between episodes 3 & 4.

Where can I download Commander Keen 1?
[url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=1keen131&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=1keen131&b=orig[/url]

Where can I download Commander Keen 2?
I won't tell you. It's illegal. You can still buy CK1-5 from 3DRealms.com. If you already have CK2, you can download the patch which will upgrade your CK2 game.
Upgrade Version 1.0 to 1.31 - [url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=2keen131&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=2keen131&b=orig[/url]

Where can I download Commander Keen 3?
I won't tell you. It's illegal. You can still buy CK1-5 from 3DRealms.com. If you already have CK3, you can download the patch which will upgrade your CK3 game.
Upgrade Version 1.0 to 1.31 - [url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=3keen131&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=3keen131&b=orig[/url]

Where can I download Commander Keen 4?
[url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=4keen14&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=4keen14&b=orig[/url]

Where can I download Commander Keen 5?
I won't tell you. It's illegal. You can still buy CK1-5 from 3DRealms.com. If you already have CK5, you can download the patch which will upgrade your CK5 game.
Upgrade any version to Version 1.4 - [url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=5keen14&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=5keen14&b=orig[/url]

Where can I download Commander Keen 6?
I won't tell you. It's illegal. There is no longer a legal way to obtain CK6. If you already have CK6, you can download the patches which will upgrade your CK6 game. Or you can download the 3-Level Demo.
Demo Version - [url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=6keend&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=6keend&b=orig[/url]
Upgrade Version 1.0 to 1.4 - [url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=6keen14&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=6keen14&b=orig[/url]
Upgrade CGA Keen 6 from ID Anthology to EGA Keen 6 Version 1.0 - [url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=6cgaegapatch&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=...tch&b=orig[/url]

Where can I download Keen Dreams?
I won't tell you. It's illegal. There is no longer a legal way to obtain Keen Dreams. Although you can download the two shareware versions of the game.
[url=http://www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=dkeen113&b=orig]www.spatang.com/dl.php?a=dkeen113&b=orig[/url]

Where can I download the Commander Keen for Gameboy Color rom?
I won't tell you. It's illegal. Go out there and buy it for your Gameboy Color
or Gameboy Advance! (If you have one!)

There are TWO Princess Lindseys? Where can I find the other one?
One is in 'Hillville'. The second Lindsey is at the top of the 'Chasm of Chills'.

How do you get all those water drops & Lifewater Flasks in 'Lifewater Oasis' without cheating?
The thing is... you can't!

How do I get the alternative ending in Keen 5?
Break the secret fuse at the very top of 'Korath III Base'. Once you finish the game, the ending will
be a little different...

Oooh, the 'F' word is in Keen 2? Where can I find it?
The word can be found if you look really hard in the level 'Paris Tantalus Rays', it's written in the Standard Galactic Alphabet, and is written in those thin yellow platforms. And the word isn't spelt as f**k, it's spelt as fucl.

How do I get Keen to moon me in CK4?
In the 'Pyramid of the Moons', stand on a moon and wait for a few seconds. Keen will moon you.
Afterwards, he won't moon you again unless you die and re-enter the level.

Is Commander Keen 2000 an official Keen game?
Of course not! Sure, iD are a bunch of "Keen Murderers", but surely their games aren't THAT
dismal.

Yeah, well, is Commander Keen 3000 out yet?
No, A.R had given up on it a LONG time ago.

What about Isis II, how's that going?
It's dead. 'Nuff said.

Where can I find Keen in Doom II?
Try Level 32.

Do Dopefish really eat Sprites?
No, they eat Schoolfish & CK.

How do I detonate the 'Quantum Explosion Dynamo' in the last level of CK5?
Try exploding a Shikadi Mine onto it.

What are those little Scottish dudes called?
Scotties.

What do you call those rocks in CK4?
Mimrocks.

What do you call those mines in CK4?
Mines. (No, Xky, i'm not talking about the Shikadi Mines in CK5!)

How about those scary blue birds?
Birds.

My game crashes when I get to the secret level in CK5?! Help me!?
Try playing in 'Normal' or 'Hard' difficulty. Otherwise, upgrade your game to version 1.4

Where can I find CK in Bio Menace?
Play episode 2 of Bio Menace, and you will eventually have to run into Keen to complete a certain
level in the game.

Do Bio Menace & CK use the same engine?
Pretty much.

Do Monster Bash & CK use the same engine?
NO!

I can't play CK6 because it prompts me to guess name of a certain monster(s)!
That means you downloaded it illegally... So I can't & WON'T help you with that!

Where can I download SKF1?
Super Keen Fighter 2 is the first SKP game.

I DON'T KNOW HOW TO USE TED5!
Oh for the love of... PRACTICE!

I'm stuck in the second level of Keen5! How come I can't fall into those holes in the ground?
Press down, and then jump (by pressing control).

How do I kill that vorticon in that castle level in Keen 1?
Shoot it about 100 times, or shoot the rope holding that large
block, and it will squish the Vorticon Commander.

How do I shoot? I've pushed all the buttons and none of them shoots!
Press Control-Alt at the same time whilst playing CK1-3.
Press Alt to shoot whilst playing Keen Dreams.
Press Spacebar to shoot whilst playing CK4-6.

Help me! I don't have a 'Control' key!
Try 'Ctrl'.

What the hell is a spacebar? Is it some sort of level in the game?
No, it's the 'long' button on your keyboard.

Why is Commander Keen wandering around a planet with no atmosphere with the only protection being his helmet?
How do YOU know that the planet has no atmosphere?

Man, I'm thirsty... can you give me some ice cold orange soft drink?
No.

How is 'Shikadi' pronounced?
Shih-kah-dee

Why is Keen so pale?
He's xenophobic.

Why does Keen die when being touched once?
He's xenophobic.

Should Keen have white or coloured skin in the fangame I'm working on?
Few suggestions : [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-smile.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-shucks.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-gimp.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-rasta.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-dopekeen.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-halloween.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-sick.gif[/img] [img]http://www.geocities.com/apogeekeen/20kbsig.txt[/img]
